evel":"high","aiAnalysisSummary":"The application presents a high risk due to a 0% verification rate of submitted documents and missing essential demographic information such as nationality. Without verified credentials or identity confirmation, the authenticity of the applicant's academic intent and background cannot be established.","blockchainHash":null,"blockchainTxId":null,"qrCodeData":null,"visaNumber":null,"grantedAt":null,"expiryDate":null,"denialReason":"your bank staemnt","officerNotes":"hi","renewalReminderSent":false,"createdAt":"2026-03-11T09:57:27.079Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-11T10:01:07.587Z"},{"id":1,"userId":7,"applicationType":"new","visaType":"student","purposeOfVisit":"My name is Naresh Kumar, and I am writing this letter to support my application for a student visa to study in Canada. I have been accepted into the Bachelor of Computer Science program at XYZ University starting in September 2026.\n\nI have always been passionate about technology and software development. Studying in Canada will provide me with access to high-quality education, modern research facilities, and international exposure that will help me develop my technical skills and professional knowledge.\n\nMy parents will financially support my education and living expenses during my studies. I have attached all the necessary documents, including my admission letter, financial statements, academic transcripts, and passport copies.\n\nAfter completing my studies, I intend to return to my home country and apply the knowledge and skills I gained to contribute to the technology sector.\n\nI respectfully request you to consider my application and grant me a student visa. Thank you for your time and consideration.","destinationCountry":"China","intendedEntryDate":"2026-03-12","intendedExitDate":"2026-03-31","status":"granted","currentStage":6,"riskScore":88,"riskLevel":"high","aiAnalysisSummary":"A critical discrepancy exists between the stated destination country (China) and the purpose of visit (Canada), indicating potential fraudulent use of template documentation. The risk is further elevated by a low document verification rate, with only one out of four documents confirmed as authentic.","blockchainHash":"fb9456904898bbdd43d9df79d4c7b2e57f398232a28c480ceb7c7cb660b1c631","blockchainTxId":"0xb37846a476cd148c6850ad9ab44d8bb4","qrCodeData":"{\"visaNumber\":\"VZ20263C262956\",\"hash\":\"fb9456904898bbdd43d9df79d4c7b2e57f398232a28c480ceb7c7cb660b1c631\",\"txId\":\"0xb37846a476cd148c6850ad9ab44d8bb4\",\"blockIndex\":1,\"holder\":\"pasu\",\"visaType\":\"student\",\"expiresAt\":\"2027-03-10\",\"valid\":true}","visaNumber":"VZ20263C262956","grantedAt":"2026-03-10T03:05:58.251Z","expiryDate":"2027-03-10","denialReason":null,"officerNotes":"i think he had valid raeason jhuhuhjiji","renewalReminderSent":false,"createdAt":"2026-03-09T12:42:42.546Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-10T05:09:18.959Z"}]
